href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533826\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533826\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 07, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xok1665702686298.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xok1665702686298.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xok1665702686298.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xok1665702686298\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Open a Main\n      Development Object for Editing</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xok1665702686298__open_a_main_development_object_for_editing_17026\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Each main development object is opened in its own editor.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xok1665702686298__section_lcg_ccf_jzb\">You can open a main development object in the following\n            ways:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xok1665702686298__ul_vcg_ccf_jzb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1511e1_d1512e1_d1513e1\">In the Main U-Bar, browse or search for an object,\n               or enter a complete URL for an object. See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fii1695716579859.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fii1695716579859.html\" title=\"Use the Main U-Bar to locate and open development objects for editing. You can browse and search for objects by object type and name, or enter a complete object URL. As you enter text, the U-Bar offers suggestions that are appropriate to the current context.\">Find and Open Objects Using the Main U-Bar</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1514e1_d1515e1_d1516e1\">In the Project Editor, double-click a main\n               development object in the Structure pane, or choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Open</span> from\n               the context menu.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1517e1_d1518e1_d1519e1\">In the Component Editor, you can: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xok1665702686298__ul_wcg_ccf_jzb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1520e1_d1521e1_d1522e1\">Right-click a modeled entity in the Model tab\n                     of the Resource Browser and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Open</span>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1523e1_d1524e1_d1525e1\">Double-click an inherited ProcScript module in\n                     the Compiled Module Inspector to open the object where it is defined.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1526e1_d1527e1_d1528e1\">For signatures, DTDs, most global objects, language\n               setups, and modeled properties, click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More Editors</span> in the\n               upper right corner of the Uniface IDE and select the type of object.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1529e1_d1530e1_d1531e1\">To open a palette of templates, you can: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xok1665702686298__ul_xcg_ccf_jzb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1532e1_d1533e1_d1534e1\">Select a Template in the Resource Browser,\n                     right click and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Open</span>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xok1665702686298__li_d1535e1_d1536e1_d1537e1\">In the U-Bar, select an object type and then\n                     enter the word <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">palette</kbd>.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"xok1665702686298__note_ycg_ccf_jzb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>  Note: This is only possible if the logical\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">ALLOW_BROWSE_TEMPLATES=1</code> is present in the\n                     <span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.asn</span> assignment file.</div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533826\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533826\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Open a Main Development Object for Editing Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 07, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Open a Main Development Object for Editing Each main development object is opened in its own editor. You can open a main development object in the following ways: In the Main U-Bar, browse or search for an object, or enter a complete URL for an object. See Find and Open Objects Using the Main U-Bar . In the Project Editor, double-click a main development object in the Structure pane, or choose Open from the context menu. In the Component Editor, you can: Right-click a modeled entity in the Model tab of the Resource Browser and choose Open . Double-click an inherited ProcScript module in the Compiled Module Inspector to open the object where it is defined. For signatures, DTDs, most global objects, language setups, and modeled properties, click More Editors in the upper right corner of the Uniface IDE and select the type of object. To open a palette of templates, you can: Select a Template in the Resource Browser, right click and choose Open . In the U-Bar, select an object type and then enter the word palette . Note: Note: This is only possible if the logical ALLOW_BROWSE_TEMPLATES=1 is present in the ide.asn assignment file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}